"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>People of high rank who therefore had great power and importance.</p>\n<h2>Nobles were of high rank</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:14\">EST 1:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:6-Prov25:7\">PRO 25:6–25:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:25\">JDG 5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:8\">1KI 21:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:11\">1KI 21:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:12\">2KI 24:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr23:20\">2CH 23:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:14\">NEH 4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:19\">NEH 4:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:5\">NEH 7:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth5:11\">EST 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:20\">JER 27:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:12\">LUK 19:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:26\">1CO 1:26</a></p>\n<h2>Nobles had great power and importance</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:1-Dan5:3\">DAN 5:1–5:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:13\">JDG 5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam10:2-2Sam10:3\">2SA 10:2–10:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr19:2-1Chr19:3\">1CH 19:2–19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:3\">EST 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:11\">EST 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:16\">EST 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:21\">EST 1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:18\">EST 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:3\">EST 9:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:9\">PSA 47:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:15-Prov8:16\">PRO 8:15–8:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:3\">JER 14:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:7\">JON 3:7</a></p>\n<h2>Nobles' abuse of their rank and power</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:6-Neh5:7\">NEH 5:6–5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:12\">NEH 5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:5\">NEH 3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:17\">NEH 13:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:2\">EZK 34:2</a></p>\n<h2>God's judgment of nobles who abused their power</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:18-Job34:19\">JOB 34:18–34:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:20-Job12:21\">JOB 12:20–12:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:40\">PSA 107:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:6-Ps149:8\">PSA 149:6–149:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:13-Isa5:14\">ISA 5:13–5:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:12\">ISA 34:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:12\">EZK 17:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:10\">NAM 3:10</a></p>",
